law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 336, effective January 1, 1975. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 108, sec. 1, effective June 17, 1954. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1209, 1211, 1376a.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Obtaining money by false personation -- Personating another in legal acts -- Fraudulently displaying badge of organization.
